Whoever wrote the review that said this DVD had good quality concert footage was trying to be funny, I guess. There is not a single song here, just a few seconds of low-res ancient concert footage. This is a British import, with British talking heads explaining what Bruce means to them. It is dull, has zero new information, and was geared to make money from the multitude of Bruce fans, of which I am one. I threw the DVD in the trash after watching it because I knew I'd never want to watch it again. The reviewer mentioned above who likened this DVD to the London Calling concert is either pulling a mean-spirited prank on Bruce fans or on strong hallucinogens...or both.
